           move      spaces               to   v-key                  .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Prezzo d'acquisto                           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-prz-pes-000      thru acc-prz-pes-999        .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-rig    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-cor-reg-900.
       acc-cor-reg-300.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
