      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-per-sco-000      thru acc-per-sco-999        .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-rig    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-cor-reg-900.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-cor-reg-200.
       acc-cor-reg-400.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Data di aggiornamento                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-uda-pes-000      thru acc-uda-pes-999        .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-rig    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-cor-reg-900.
