                     go to acc-per-sco-999.
           subtract  1                    from w-cix-ctr-001          .
           go to     acc-per-sco-100.
       acc-per-sco-670.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Down o Return                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-per-sco-999.
       acc-per-sco-700.
